{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777798558925,"sessionID":"ses_212f7942affeOT4DsTKU0nvmZ9","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_bdrk_01A1LKKTNZ28drN1YaZmmzKG","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"grep -i \"forward\\|fwd\" cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nfor line in sys.stdin:\n    j = json.loads(line)\n    if 'forward' in j['title'].lower() or 'fwd' in j['title'].lower():\n        print(j['id'], j['outcome'], '-', j['title'][:100])\n\"","description":"Find prior hypotheses mentioning forwarding"},"output":"hyp-20260503-002-r5s1 broken - ALU-integrated JAL/JALR link: fold pc+4 into pre-ALU operand muxes, delete post-ALU link mux and ded\nhyp-20260503-001-r10s0 broken - Gate reg_write at ID for rd==0 to shorten forward_unit priority encoder\nhyp-20260503-002-r11s1 regression - Split-origin regfile commit: ALU writes from EX/MEM, loads from MEM/WB, shrinking the forward mux tr\n","metadata":{"output":"hyp-20260503-002-r5s1 broken - ALU-integrated JAL/JALR link: fold pc+4 into pre-ALU operand muxes, delete post-ALU link mux and ded\nhyp-20260503-001-r10s0 broken - Gate reg_write at ID for rd==0 to shorten forward_unit priority encoder\nhyp-20260503-002-r11s1 regression - Split-origin regfile commit: ALU writes from EX/MEM, loads from MEM/WB, shrinking the forward mux tr\n","exit":0,"description":"Find prior hypotheses mentioning forwarding","truncated":false},"title":"Find prior hypotheses mentioning forwarding","time":{"start":1777798558920,"end":1777798558924}},"metadata":{"openrouter":{"reasoning_details":[]}},"id":"prt_ded0d31b3001FShx8NBTeXQjRQ","sessionID":"ses_212f7942affeOT4DsTKU0nvmZ9","messageID":"msg_ded0d2bee001M5mBIVOSHneaqL"}}
