{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1777786164855,"sessionID":"ses_213b401fbffeeZdL7EzK147fQT","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_bdrk_01HHRGTAjAznTBhVm9NYrx3p","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\nwith open('cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl') as f:\n    for line in f:\n        d = json.loads(line)\n        print(d['id'], '|', d['category'], '|', d['outcome'], '|', d.get('delta_pct','n/a'), '|', d['title'][:70])\n\"","description":"Summarize all prior hypotheses"},"output":"baseline-bench-46e45dd | micro_opt | improvement | 0.0 | Baseline retest for cores/bench\nhyp-20260503-001-r1s0 | micro_opt | improvement | 9.47 | Share single 33x33 signed multiplier across MUL/MULH/MULHU/MULHSU\nhyp-20260503-002-r1s1 | structural | regression | 0.0 | Split ALU: move MUL/DIV into multi-cycle execution unit with EX stall \nhyp-20260503-003-r1s2 | predictor | regression | -11.64 | IF-stage JAL direct-jump + backward-taken static branch predictor\nhyp-20260503-001-r2s0 | micro_opt | regression | -4.1 | Share a single 33-bit subtractor across ADD/SUB/SLT/SLTU and branch co\nhyp-20260503-002-r2s1 | structural | regression | -17.54 | Decoupled IF/ID via 1-entry prefetch skid buffer to absorb iStall bubb\nhyp-20260503-003-r2s2 | predictor | regression | 0.0 | Registered 16-entry BTB indexed by PC (off the fetch BRAM critical pat\nhyp-20260503-001-r3s0 | micro_opt | broken | n/a | Regfile as GW2AR distributed-RAM (SSRAM) — drop reset-loop to free ~1k\nhyp-20260503-002-r3s1 | structural | regression | -5.66 | Pre-mux write-back value in MEM stage: collapse WB's mem_to_reg mux in\nhyp-20260503-003-r3s2 | predictor | regression | 0.0 | Tiny 4-entry Return Address Stack (RAS) with ID-stage speculative redi\n","metadata":{"output":"baseline-bench-46e45dd | micro_opt | improvement | 0.0 | Baseline retest for cores/bench\nhyp-20260503-001-r1s0 | micro_opt | improvement | 9.47 | Share single 33x33 signed multiplier across MUL/MULH/MULHU/MULHSU\nhyp-20260503-002-r1s1 | structural | regression | 0.0 | Split ALU: move MUL/DIV into multi-cycle execution unit with EX stall \nhyp-20260503-003-r1s2 | predictor | regression | -11.64 | IF-stage JAL direct-jump + backward-taken static branch predictor\nhyp-20260503-001-r2s0 | micro_opt | regression | -4.1 | Share a single 33-bit subtractor across ADD/SUB/SLT/SLTU and branch co\nhyp-20260503-002-r2s1 | structural | regression | -17.54 | Decoupled IF/ID via 1-entry prefetch skid buffer to absorb iStall bubb\nhyp-20260503-003-r2s2 | predictor | regression | 0.0 | Registered 16-entry BTB indexed by PC (off the fetch BRAM critical pat\nhyp-20260503-001-r3s0 | micro_opt | broken | n/a | Regfile as GW2AR distributed-RAM (SSRAM) — drop reset-loop to free ~1k\nhyp-20260503-002-r3s1 | structural | regression | -5.66 | Pre-mux write-back value in MEM stage: collapse WB's mem_to_reg mux in\nhyp-20260503-003-r3s2 | predictor | regression | 0.0 | Tiny 4-entry Return Address Stack (RAS) with ID-stage speculative redi\n","exit":0,"description":"Summarize all prior hypotheses","truncated":false},"title":"Summarize all prior hypotheses","time":{"start":1777786164851,"end":1777786164854}},"metadata":{"openrouter":{"reasoning_details":[]}},"id":"prt_dec501266001hefvOLEnJK0Rtc","sessionID":"ses_213b401fbffeeZdL7EzK147fQT","messageID":"msg_dec500c30001cNqZYgU3Jq7UW1"}}
